data.description: Beautiful 3BR, 2BA Rancher, attached 2 car garage on over half unrestricted acres (0.65). Large covered front porch is inviting. Entry offers an oversized foyer. Spacious kitchen with island and plenty of storage. Open living floor plan is cozy and the large windows, living and dining area overlooks fenced backyard and pool. Master has his/her vanity, spa soaker tub, walk-in shower and private 'water closet'' Attic is plenty spacious enough and could easily be finished out for more living space. All city utilities and the location is ideal for quick trips to Athens or Sweetwater.
